title: Hurty Birds
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth recap Monday night’s double header. What is it about prime-time that scares Kirk Cousins? And the Bills completely embarrassed the Titans, setting up an exciting week 3 matchup with the Dolphins. Plus, they reveal their Winners & Woofs for Week 2!
